        <a name="003099"></a>
        
        <h4>My Wii number</h4>
        <p>is <strong>8208 9478 2034 3274</strong>.</p>

<p>If you want to see my scruffy, portly (and endearingly accurate) Mii strut his stuff in your Mii Parade, or just want to send rude messages to my TV screen, let me know your friend code.</p>
