<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/sep/19/">&#x27a0;</a> September 19, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="game_informer_o" >

        
        <a name="002939"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.gameinformer.com/News/Story/200609/N06.0915.1324.09291.htm">Game Informer Online:  Will Wii Be Disappointed Again?</a></h4>

        

        <p>Are us Nintendo fanboys just setting ourselves up for disappointment again?  Frankly, I&#8217;ve never been disappointed with Nintendo consoles:  They were the only places to play Donkey Kong Country or Pikmin, and well worth the price of admittance.</p>

