        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.engadget.com/2006/09/14/live-at-nintendos-nyc-wii-press-conference/">Live at Nintendo&#39;s NYC Wii press conference - Engadget</a></h4>

        

        <p>The Wii details are out:  Launches Nov 19th (two days after PS3), $250 including one remote+nunchuck and Wii Sports, Extra remote+nunchuck for $60.  From the download service, NES games will be $5, SNES games $8, N64 games $10.  I can&#8217;t bloody wait!</p>

